30
00:01:49,374 --> 00:01:54,311
Please take part to see and evaluate
what you have learned so far.

31
00:01:54,731 --> 00:01:57,093
The hard deadline is
November 9th.

32
00:01:57,783 --> 00:02:00,929
And please also send us
your questions to the Forum.

33
00:02:00,929 --> 00:02:03,486
We'll be collecting these
and answering them

34
00:02:03,486 --> 00:02:07,589
during a Q&A studio session
in the last week of this course.

35
